sentences: Thomas Heberer (born September 24, 1965, in Schleswig, Germany) is a trumpeter, quarter-tone trumpeter, cornetist, keyboardist and composer, primarily focused on jazz, creative improvised music and contemporary chamber music.
From 1984 to 1987, he studied at conservatory with Manfred Schoof at the Cologne University of Music.
